                  </hi>. Aged 27.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18440610-1585-punishment-34" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18440610-1585-punishment-34" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1585-18440610 t18440610-1585-punishment-34"></join>Transported for Ten Years more</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
